kip this step** to skip configuring the application. If you choose to skip this step, end users have to perform any required first-use tasks such as accepting any license agreements and first-use questions.\n\n## Related topics\n\n\n[Sequencer Wizard - Package Accelerator (AppV 4.6 SP1)](sequencer-wizard---package-accelerator--appv-46-sp1-.md)\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n"}